In this practice using the tutorials that have been showed to us before I:

Created an Usuario class (with its own file) using __construct, setterts and getters,
then i called to instance it.
Also, using the Setters function I changed the value.

The output its shown in a simple html page with no css for design.

To see the output I used the terminal to cd into the folder where these project its and then used: 
    php -S localhost:8000
After that i used http://localhost:8000/index.php on my browser to check the output.